text.section:
The cabinet shall by June 30, 2003:
Establish certification terms, conditions, and length of time the certification is valid;
Establish terms, conditions, and standards for recertification;
Establish fees for certification and recertification; and
Develop a certification document.

The cabinet and the Kentucky Cooperative Extension Service shall by June 30, 2003:
Develop an examination document;
Establish examination subject matter;
Establish criteria for program completion; and
Establish fees for the pilot microprocessing program and the microprocessing program.
